   â†’ Analyze changes for documentation impact
   â†’ If high/medium priority triggers found: Ask "ğŸ“š Update docs first? (u/r/s/c)"
   
   If unstaged changes present AND user hasn't explicitly requested them:
   â†’ Ask: "Include unstaged changes? (y/n/review)"
   
